      "beast_baseline": "I'm a bit confused. I'm trying to study for a real music exam, so the metaphors are making it harder to focus. Can we just stick to the actual theory? Can you explain how the \"Circle of Fourths\" works in relation to this, and how it helps with finding minor keys?",
